rd-number-of-u-s-jews-to-rally-in-d-c-in-show-of-support-for-israels-war-on-hamas/0000018b-cd27-dd11-a19f-edf7b4350000</guid></item><item><title>加沙的记者争先恐后地记录以色列的轰炸。数十人付出了生命的代价</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-14/ty-article/.premium/gazas-journalist-rush-to-document-israeli-bombardments-dozens-have-paid-with-their-lives/0000018b-cd06-d423-affb-ffa7e85d0000</link><description>许多人还失去了家人，家园遭到破坏或毁坏，办公室也遭到袭击。随着破坏的加剧，越来越多的报道是由普通人用即兴的方法进行的</description><pubDate>Tue, 14 Nov 2023 10:42:08 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-14/ty-article/.premium/gazas-journalist-rush-to-document-israeli-bombardments-dozens-have-paid-with-their-lives/0000018b-cd06-d423-affb-ffa7e85d0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列狂欢大屠杀受害者因未完全皈依犹太教而被埋在墓地外</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-14/ty-article/.premium/victim-of-rave-massacre-buried-outside-cemetery-due-to-incomplete-conversion-to-judaism/0000018b-cd3c-df9a-ab8b-dffccc370000</link><description>由于尚未完成皈依犹太教的课程，10 月 7 日在诺瓦音乐节上遇害的阿丽娜·法拉哈蒂 (Alina Falahati) 被拒绝埋葬在犹太公墓。以色列拉比官员表示，“这是一个错误”</description><pubDate>Tue, 14 Nov 2023 10:14:46 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-14/ty-article/.premium/victim-of-rave-massacre-buried-outside-cemetery-due-to-incomplete-conversion-to-judaism/0000018b-cd3c-df9a-ab8b-dffccc370000</guid></item><item><title>加沙简史：五千年的冲突</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-14/ty-article-magazine/.premium/a-short-history-of-gaza-5-000-years-of-strife/0000017f-e4ae-d7b2-a77f-e7afb6a40000</link><description>正如先知所预言的那样，这片土地自古以来就一直在争夺</description><pubDate>Tue, 14 Nov 2023 10:13:21 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-14/ty-article-magazine/.premium/a-short-history-of-gaza-5-000-years-of-strife/0000017f-e4ae-d7b2-a77f-e7afb6a40000</guid></item><item><title>中国、伊朗和阿拉伯国家谴责以色列部长关于在加沙投放核弹的声明</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-14/ty-article/china-iran-arab-nations-condemn-israeli-ministers-nuclear-bomb-statement/0000018b-cce6-df9a-ab8b-deeeb98f0000</link><description>极右翼部长阿米猜·埃利亚胡在电台采访中的即兴评论引发了争议和国际关注。世界各地的官员称其“极其不负责任且令人不安”，“对地区稳定构成重大威胁”</description><pubDate>Tue, 14 Nov 2023 09:34:45 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-14/ty-article/china-iran-arab-nations-condemn-israeli-ministers-nuclear-bomb-statement/0000018b-cce6-df9a-ab8b-deeeb98f0000</guid></item><item><title>巴勒斯坦人：以色列国防军西岸袭击中七人死亡；以色列军队证实一名被俘士兵在加沙死亡</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-14/ty-article-live/body-of-canadian-israel-peace-activist-idd-hamas-publishes-video-of-captive-idf-soldier/0000018b-cc03-d57d-afff-cff3a1f90000</link><description>巴勒斯坦人称，以色列国防军在约旦河西岸城市图尔卡姆的炮火造成七名巴勒斯坦人死亡 ■ 以色列国防军证实周一出现在哈马斯视频中的以色列士兵死亡 ■ 以色列国防军证实周一有两名士兵在加沙战斗中丧生 ■ MKs 呼吁将加沙人转移到其他国家《华尔街日报》中的国家 ■ 以色列国防部长加兰特：哈马斯已失去对加沙的控制 ■ 至少 1,200 名以色列人在哈马斯大屠杀中丧生，239 名人质在加沙被扣 ■ 哈马斯控制的加沙卫生部：自战争开始以来已有 11,240 人死亡</description><pubDate>Tue, 14 Nov 2023 04:19:09 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-14/ty-article-live/body-of-canadian-israel-peace-activist-idd-hamas-publishes-video-of-captive-idf-soldier/0000018b-cc03-d57d-afff-cff3a1f90000</guid></item><item><title>以色列军队在加沙取得进展，但哈马斯投降还远未到来</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-14/ty-article/.premium/israels-military-is-making-headway-in-gaza-but-hamas-surrender-is-far-from-imminent/0000018b-ca6f-d8c7-a59b-df6f80560000</link><description>考虑到国际上的限制，以色列国防军的愿望可能无法实现，但对于加沙的以色列军官来说，只有击败哈马斯，行动才会结束</description><pubDate>Tue, 14 Nov 2023 04:00:21 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-14/ty-article/.premium/israels-military-is-making-headway-in-gaza-but-hamas-surrender-is-far-from-imminent/0000018b-ca6f-d8c7-a59b-df6f80560000</guid></item><item><title>失踪的以色列裔加拿大和平活动人士维维安·西尔弗 (Vivian Silver) 确认在 10 月 7 日哈马斯袭击中丧生</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-